00:17:24.400 --> 00:17:26.280
Kung hindi mo sinamantala ang sitwasyon,

00:17:26.280 --> 00:17:28.000
Hindi sana nawala ang anak ko.

00:17:28.079 --> 00:17:30.080
Kaya't narito si Pei Xi upang bayaran ang kanyang buhay.

00:17:30.880 --> 00:17:31.960
Ibig mong sabihin

00:17:31.960 --> 00:17:35.020
